{"tid":2172564,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇絲打都有脫髮問題","createTime":"2020-08-24T16:53:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T14:59:09.000Z","uid":302105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1eb36c9b03a3660e318dc4c4934eafb63cc3da0d","tid":2172564,"uid":302105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T16:53:52.000Z","msg":"我宜家先18<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但呢排洗頭吹完頭甩勁多頭髮<br />\n大約20條(以前甩超少ard5-10條)<br />\n每日洗頭都會用少少護髮素<br />\nShampoo同conditioner都係用ess__tial<br />\n以前一路都用開 只係呢排開始甩得多<br />\n明明冇學返放緊sem break又冇壓力<br />\n(但嚟m會情緒唔穩定)<br />\n體重冇暴升暴跌<br />\n有check過頭頂有冇禿 咩事都冇<br />\n究竟係正常新陳代謝定咩事<br />\n本身髮量已經少同薄<br />\n同埋呢一年內有電+染髮大約5次<br />\n不過一路都冇乜點甩 係呢一個月開始甩得好勁<br />\n我唔想18歲就冇頭髮呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a971305af419ab787c01e36c6578775b2d500129","tid":2172564,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:02:20.000Z","msg":"你尾三嗰行咪講咗原因，<br />\n一路冇事同你依家有事係冇衝突，<br />\n好多嘢都係儲埋儲埋就爆"},{"pid":"d91b8ed0c1211c20385303d3e2e572d2f8e79b3d","tid":2172564,"uid":213705,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T21:07:26.000Z","msg":"每日甩50-70條都係正常範圍"},{"pid":"3dab8beae242f2ed47a51dab9e51ddace33cb54d","tid":2172564,"uid":223672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T07:36:31.000Z","msg":"唔好洗太密同唔好電染住 養返好先"},{"pid":"f76914e41f13f20c6de57876b2c4cc2a47b731b7","tid":2172564,"uid":345024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:43:15.000Z","msg":"你嗰個牌子真係垃圾😂😂😂"},{"pid":"ad9f6dab8c10f3ad404e5fb6b4f2aa85b3d07d1b","tid":2172564,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:45:41.000Z","msg":"又電又染"},{"pid":"e70247f0f0988c8ba371aa2e22c1ecae7ee2eaf5","tid":2172564,"uid":1593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:48:46.000Z","msg":"一日甩100條係正常<br />\n試一過洗一次頭甩60條(執番地下d頭髮數)"},{"pid":"5c68c0761ff79ce234